European Central Bank Said to Purchase Italian Government Securities Today

-- B y   K e i t h   J e n k i n s
-- 
2011-08-19T09:45:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/european-central-bank-said-to-purchase-italian-government-securities-today.html
The  European Central Bank  bought
Italian government bonds, according to three people with
knowledge of the transactions.  The purchases were in small amounts, said one of the
people, who asked not to be identified because the deals are
confidential.  A spokesman for the central bank declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Keith Jenkins in London at 
